{"tid":1998301,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"傳聞藍軍750萬歐元預定「新卡卡」","createTime":"2020-05-02T09:57:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-03T11:08:45.000Z","uid":77132,"like":5,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"16d7f2c97a352ce626c99993c4512f52f6834e24","tid":1998301,"uid":77132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T09:57:18.000Z","msg":"據巴西傳媒今日報導，車路士已從聖保羅高價簽下該隊的17歲天才前鋒Lucas Piazon。而在巴西國內Lucas Piazon則有「新卡卡」的美譽...<br />\n<br />\n        首先我們需要指出，車路士購入的Lucas Piazon，與上個月在南美U-20錦標賽中表現搶眼的Lucas Marcelinho雖然共同效力于巴西聖保羅，但並非為同一名球員。因為從球技、速度和外貌都讓人不由得聯想起從聖保羅走出的世界級球星卡卡，Lucas Piazon在巴西國內也有著「新卡卡」的美譽。<br />\n<br />\n       Lucas Piazon在今年年初剛剛年滿17歲，迄今為止也僅僅代表聖保羅參加過一場正式比賽。然而這名小傢伙的天賦和球技卻已經得到了「足球王國」的廣泛認可，被視為是巴西國內最新湧現出來的未來之星。在其代表巴西U-17國家隊參加的首場比賽中，他就通過入球幫助巴西4-3擊敗委內瑞拉。<br />\n<br />\n       其實早在2年前，代表巴西隊出戰南美U-15錦標賽的時候，Lucas Piazon的名字就開始得到了關注。在2009年的賽事中，他以10個入球的成績成為了錦標賽的最佳射手。<br />\n<br />\n       據巴西《環球體育》報導，面向全球來搜羅足球人才的車路士已經將觸角伸及Lucas Piazon的身上。藍軍即將以750萬歐元的價格從聖保羅購入球員，並將球員暫時交給聖保羅代為培養一年，2011年底等到球員年滿18歲後再將其領回倫敦。<br />\n<br />\n       在車路士出價之前，意甲的祖雲達斯據說也曾接觸過Lucas Piazon。在征得球會的同意之後，雙方卻在討論球員個人條款時發生了嚴重的分歧，最終讓轉會談判破產。(<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=eQX%2BqlmYp67lP1AM6ayufV8MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=a6b2e0ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢啲新仔要磨練下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de3c7fe836d302d00610a0255641092e9e5ee981","tid":1998301,"uid":57232,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T10:00:06.000Z","msg":"呢件20歲之後無進步過<br />\n最勁已經係法蘭克福嗰期"},{"pid":"c9d3a3ccdf1b7de64c8ea372d9bdde8af46720e8","tid":1998301,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T10:10:59.000Z","msg":"Marcelinho<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2a5ef708ff40d6c06f1e8393d78be13e13e8d0f","tid":1998301,"uid":4574,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T10:13:14.000Z","msg":"新比利呢"},{"pid":"889e8088b8e2ee97cb23757df16203e71c037c8c","tid":1998301,"uid":34572,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b2a5ef708ff40d6c06f1e8393d78be13e13e8d0f","tid":1998301,"uid":4574,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T10:13:14.000Z","msg":"新比利呢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T10:15:55.000Z","msg":"羅賓奴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"909812f57a26069066b62c51825de5466e6e5576","tid":1998301,"uid":5649,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T10:17:18.000Z","msg":"呢件外借357年必成大器"},{"pid":"72aff8e02b1a958e3559b10e7033054c0866e12d","tid":1998301,"uid":63913,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T10:41:32.000Z","msg":"依件𡃁仔個樣同位都同卡卡一樣，根本係卡卡二世。二十歲前可以擔大旗。順手買埋巴西個後生仔尼馬，組成森巴前場。"},{"pid":"8bd922b4e3d6e5256eecd4766e13d16c8653b69a","tid":1998301,"uid":165817,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T10:49:40.000Z","msg":"呢個勁，應該會至少喺車仔留7,8年"},{"pid":"9c5a6fdd7bd9f1025839bf63b8d420365163e04d","tid":1998301,"uid":3962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T10:50:57.000Z","msg":"新。新。新卡卡"},{"pid":"2279f2b23077723ec553671588157f075ef832b0","tid":1998301,"uid":178382,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T10:53:57.000Z","msg":"我由細睇到佢踢波大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f29f9f7c2bc66e91ed64d2aba83038654ee6bdf9","tid":1998301,"uid":2500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T11:00:27.000Z","msg":"呢件真係巴西未來領軍人物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁細個已經咁好技術 大個仲得了"},{"pid":"f